<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/bridget-phillipson> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Bridget Phillipson was appointed Secretary of State for Education on 5 July 2024 and Minister for Women and Equalities on 8 July 2024. She was elected as the Labour MP for Houghton and Sunderland South in May 2010."@en .
